data.description: Beautifully Finished Immaculate Renovated Cape Style Home. Large Kitchen With Oak Cabinets and An Eat-In Area. Large Utility Room Directly Off Kitchen. You Will Appreciate Entertaining In the Grand Dining Room Which Exits To the Living Room Well Lit By Large Windows. All Windows Have Been Replaced! The Second Floor Boasts A Huge Master Bedroom/Sitting Room. Two Additional Bedrooms and A Common Shared Space For Family Use. The Fourth Bedroom Is Situated On the First Floor What A Bonus! New Roof 2016, Lovely Outside Green Space For Recreation Includes Patio and Fenced In Back Yard.
